      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网执行器控制器的状态图。核心场景是：MQTT Broker触发后，控制器进入空闲状态，然后跟边缘节点握手成功后进入写入状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IDLE",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "WRITING"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我理解为：MQTT Broker作为外部触发源，指向IDLE状态。然后IDLE到WRITING的转换条件是跟EdgeNode完成AW握手，对吗？这个AW是指认证握手还是应用层握手？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IDLE",
        "WRITING",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，AW是Application Whitelist handshake，应用层白名单握手。另外WRITING完成后要回到IDLE，触发条件是写入完成，由ActuatorController本身上报。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WRITING",
        "IDLE",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主结构画出来：MQTT Broker指向IDLE，IDLE通过AW handshake转换到WRITING，WRITING再通过W complete回到IDLE。两个转换条件我都标注上对应的设备角色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IDLE",
        "WRITING",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，W complete的触发方确认一下——是ActuatorController自己完成写入后主动上报，不是EdgeNode来确认的。你刚才的标注没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WRITING",
        "IDLE",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，WRITING到IDLE的转换标注的是ActuatorController。IDLE到WRITING标注的是EdgeNode。这样逻辑就闭环了：Broker唤醒→空闲待命→EdgeNode握手后开始写入→Controller自己完事后回归空闲。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IDLE",
        "WRITING",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "结构没问题了。不过状态名建议用大写，IDLE和WRITING，这样跟工业控制系统的惯用命名保持一致。转换条件里的换行也保留，让AW handshake和EdgeNode的对应关系更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IDLE",
        "WRITING"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，状态全部大写，转换条件用换行分隔设备和握手类型。最终图结构：MQTT_Broker触发IDLE，IDLE经AW handshake（EdgeNode）进入WRITING，WRITING经W complete（ActuatorController）返回IDLE。",
